00:15.660 --> 00:16.620
It didn't actually read it.

00:16.940 --> 00:21.500
Exactly. What if the artificial intelligence essentially ignored you?

00:21.500 --> 00:36.240
And I mean, what if I told you that the billions and billions of parameters that tech companies relentlessly brag about, the very building blocks of these neural networks are completely mathematically meaningless?

00:37.200 --> 00:40.980
Today, we are tearing down the fundamental illusions of reality.

00:40.980 --> 00:45.140
Yeah, it is the absolute definition of an ontological shock.

00:45.380 --> 00:45.480
Right.

00:45.540 --> 00:52.720
The things we think are the foundational reality, you know, the clear causes and effects we rely on are actually just emergent illusions.

00:52.960 --> 00:55.880
They're masking a completely different underlying structure.

00:56.100 --> 00:59.300
And that is exactly why you are here with us today.

00:59.480 --> 01:01.120
Welcome to another Deep Dive.

